    "XAI can provide explanations for its decisions and actions in a way that can be easily understood by humans.",
    "However, we do not think that XAI is the ultimate solution, especially that it may involve privacy breach to offer explanations.",
    "Like any other technology, AI is associated with its own drawbacks, and there are always opportunities for further improvements.",
